author: rich
msg: Changed to initialize the 'cause' on every ServletException before throwing it.  This fixes the hiding of the original exception due to legacy behavior in ServletException ('rootCause' is what's initialized by the constructor -- not 'cause').

author: rgardler
msg: cache the navigation stuff for a reasonable length of time - improves performance by a *huge* amount since we don't make multple requests to the repository for relatively static documents (need to create a daisy generator with better caching)
